WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.320
The Abilities Registry gives TYPO3

2
00:00:02.340 --> 00:00:04.035
one place to describe actions

3
00:00:04.055 --> 00:00:06.000
that tools may perform.

4
00:00:06.020 --> 00:00:08.840
A developer defines the required

5
00:00:08.860 --> 00:00:12.015
input, output, permissions, and risk

6
00:00:12.035 --> 00:00:13.345
once. TYPO3 can then offer

7
00:00:13.365 --> 00:00:16.070
that action through supported interfaces,

8
00:00:16.090 --> 00:00:18.335
while policy and user permissions

9
00:00:18.355 --> 00:00:20.515
are checked before it runs.

10
00:00:20.535 --> 00:00:22.710
Actions that need review wait

11
00:00:22.730 --> 00:00:24.220
for a person, and every

12
00:00:24.240 --> 00:00:25.305
result is recorded.

13
00:00:25.325 --> 00:00:27.530
The feature page explains the

14
00:00:27.550 --> 00:00:28.800
full control flow.
